            key = "UI_BurdJournals_LoreTemplate_KrampusBellTower",
            fallback = "The bell tower rang at midnight without a rope. Every dead thing in three blocks turned its head like children hearing dinner. {{survivorName}} cried because the rhythm sounded almost festive.\n\nIf {{openerName}} reads this, keep {{supplyNoun}} wrapped, keep {{traitName}} quiet, and remember {{entryName}} before the next bell. Some invitations are shaped like songs.",
